---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🧑‍🚀 Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
			<p>
				欢迎来到官方Astro博客入门模板。就是这样 模板作为轻量级、极简风格的起点，适合任何想要构建的人 与Astro合作的个人网站、博客或作品集。
			</p>
			<p>
				这个模板已经在你的文件里配置了一些集成。你可以用Astro Integrations自定义配置，添加像Tailwind这样的工具， React，或者用Vue来处理你的项目。astro.config.mjs
			</p>
			<p>以下是一些关于如何开始使用模板的建议：</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Edit this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>Edit the site header items in <code>src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>Add your name to the footer in <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code>src/content/blog/</code></li>
				<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="#"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a href="#">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/shtrend/astro-blog-starter-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a href="#">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
